orig: He tāne i kakahutia i tētahi hate whero e tū ana kei mua i tētahi awa kei roto i tētahi taone me tētahi atu tāne e tango whakaahua kei muri i te tāne e mau ana te hate whero

caption: This is a man smiling at the photographer, behind him is a green lake
orig: He tangata tenei e menemene ana ki te kai tango whakaahua, kei muri i aa ia teetahi roto kaakaariki

caption: Red flowers next to another small tree sitting in front of a big white house or a white car
orig: Ngā putiputi whero kei te taha o tētahi atu rākau iti e noho ana kei mua i tētahi whare nui mā me tētahi waka mā rānei

caption: There are red flowers on a tree, and beyond is an old house
orig: He putiputi whero kei runga i teetahi raakau, kei tua atu teetahi whare tawhito

caption: A man sitting in his white canoe on the beach and a boy holding a large fish in the water on the ground next to the white canoe
orig: He tāne e noho ana i tōna waka mā kei te tātahi me tētahi tama e mau ana he ika nui kei roto i te wai kei runga i te oneone i te taha o te waka mā

caption: This is a boy holding an eel in his hand, behind him is a rower.
orig: He tamaiti tenei e mau ana i teetahi ika tuna ki tana ringa, kei muri i aa ia teetahi tangata hoe waka ama

caption: A red house sits on a large lake
orig: He whare whero e noho ana kei runga i tētahi roto nui

caption: This is a red parking garage, next to the lake, with a small boat on the other side
orig: He Karaati whero teenei hei pupuri waka, kei te taha o te roto, kei te taha teetahi waka iti

caption: A black and white photograph of an iron bar standing outside a building
orig: He whakaahua pango me mā o tētahi tāepa rino e tū ana kei waho o tētahi whare

caption: Rats come to the garden and the area is also fenced off
orig: E kaa mai ana nga raiti ki te maara i te poo kua taiepahia hoki te waahi nei

caption: Three people standing in front of a very large group of people clapping some blue and pink things
orig: Ngā tāngata e toru e tū ana kei mua i tētahi rōpū tangata nunui rawa atu e pakipaki ana ētahi mea kikorangi me māwhero

caption: These are three people who are standing on the floor of an event. Behind them is a photo frame of the crowd clapping and clapping their hands together.
orig: He tokotoru eenei e tuu ana ki te papa ahurewa o teetahi huihuinga nei. Kei muri i aa raatou he papa whakaahua o te marea e pakipaki ana me aa raatou paruunu pakipaki

caption: This is a seagull standing on the road eating with its mouth holding a piece of food
orig: He karoro tenei e tu ana i runga i te huarahi kai tana waha e pupuri ana ia he maramara kai

caption: These are red book covers that have been printed in Malayalam literature
orig: He uhi pukapuka whero enei kua taangia nei ki nga tuhinga o nga iwi muhirama

caption: These are herds of camels living in the sandy desert where many stones are scattered in the sand
orig: He kahui kamera enei e noho ana i te koraha oneone kua marara noa nei nga tini kohatu i te one kirikiri

caption: This is a gathering of people of Asian origin who exchange information in a large room
orig: He huihuinga tangata tenei i takea mai i Ahia e whakawhiti korero ana ratou i roto i tetahi ruma nui

caption: This is a group of people from Indian tribes who gather in the main square of the town
orig: He kahui tangata tenei no nga iwi iniana e huihui ana ratou i runga i te marae nui o te taone

caption: These are photos hanging on photo poles in the middle of the city center where the leaves are scattered.
orig: He taanga whakaahua enei e iri ana i runga i nga pou whakairi whakaahua i waenganui tonu i te pokapu o te taone kai te tuarongo ko nga rau e noho marara ana

caption: This is a black dog lying flat on the floor
orig: He kuri mangumangu tenei e takoto wharoro ana i runga i te papa

caption: This is a group of families swimming in a swimming pool, on the banks of which are two sheds where they are eating and a woman is sitting on a long chair.
orig: He kahui whanau tenei e kauhoe ana i te puna kauhoe kai ona tahataha e rua nga wharau e tu ana kai tua atu he wahine e noho ana i runga i te turu roa

caption: These are antique lamps hanging from the ceiling of the house
orig: He rama tahito enei e iri ana i te tuanui o te whare

caption: Besides, the yellow lamp is shining and the many lamps are flickering on the surface of the earth.
orig: Kai tua ko te rama wheera e tirama ana a, e wherikoriko ana hoki nga tini rama i runga i te mata o te whenua kai nga pae ko te tini o te tangata e noho ana

caption: This is a shade that covers the food soil as well as the children's playground equipment and two palm trees.
orig: He ataarangi tenei e maru ana i te oneone kai tua atu ko nga taonga kori ma nga tamariki e tu ana, a e rua hoki nga rakau nikau e tu ana

caption: This is a photo of a European city with trees in the center of the city center and people walking by.
orig: He taanga whakaahua tenei o tetahi taone o Uropi kai waenganui i te pokapu matua he rakau e ngahoro ana i ona rau a, e taki hikoi ana nga tangata

caption: This is a bird native to China that lives on the sandbar of the sea
orig: He manu kotuku tenei no nga iwi taketake o Haina e noho ana i runga i te pae one o te moana

caption: This is a red car parked in front of a wrought iron fence on one side with a red awning and white seats under the awning.
orig: He motuka whero tenei kua tau nei i mua i te taiapa rino kai tetahi taha e tu ana he whakamarumaru whero me nga turu ma kai raro iho i te whakamarumaru

caption: This is the sunset reflected in the crystal clear water of the sea.
orig: Ko te torengitanga o te ra tenei e whakaata mai ana i runga i te aiotanga o te wai o te moana e horapa mai ana

caption: Two purple contacts
orig: Eetahi paatangata waiporoporo e rua

caption: Two purple starfish on the ocean floor
orig: E rua nga ika whetuu waiporoporo kei runga i te oneone o te moana

caption: Components of a computer
orig: Nga waahanga o te rorohiko paanoho

caption: There is a computer but the cover has been removed and the internal parts are visible
orig: He rorohiko engari kua tangohia te uhi ara kei te kite i nga wahanga o roto

caption: The floor is wet from the rain
orig: Te papa kua maaku i te ua

caption: A picture of a wet hardwood floor
orig: He pikitia makaro o te papa maaro maakuu

caption: Some three clocks
orig: Eetahi karaka e toru

caption: Three old clocks showing different times hang on the wall
orig: E toru nga karaka tawhito e whakaatuu ana i nga waa rerekee e iri ana i te pakitara

caption: The sea is frozen and frozen
orig: Te moana kua huka papa , kua tio hoki

caption: Ice and glaciers are above sea level
orig: Ko te tio me te hukapapa kei runga ake i te moana

caption: Relatives are waiting by the side of the road
orig: E tatari ana ngaa whaanau ki te taha o te rori

caption: A group of people are near a shop and some cars are on the road
orig: He roopu tangata kei te taha o tetahi toa me etahi motuka kei te rori

caption: It's a cocoon flower
orig: He putiputi kookoowai

caption: A pink flower blooms from a garden nursery
orig: He putiputi maawhero e puawai mai ana i tetahi whare whakatipu maara

caption: Some red flowers
orig: Eetahi putiputi whero

caption: Three red flowers bloom from the forest
orig: E toru nga putiputi whero e puawai mai ana i te ngahere

caption: It's a sunny day
orig: He rangi kaapuapua

caption: A picture of the sky with clouds and some tall buildings
orig: He pikitia o te rangi me me nga kapua me etahi whare teitei

caption: It's a fried chicken dish
orig: He kai heihei parai

caption: Fried chicken wings are served on a plate
orig: Ko nga parirau o te heihei kua paraae hei kai ki runga i te pereti

caption: Some purple bottles
orig: Etahi ipu waiporoporo

caption: A cupboard full of purple bottles with words on them
orig: He kaapata e kii ana i nga paatara waiporoporo me etahi kupu kei runga

caption: A family sells coconut drinks
orig: He whanau e hoko inu kokonati ana

caption: A family under one roof eating coconuts
orig: He whanau kei raro i tetahi maru e kai kokonati ana

caption: An old steamer
orig: He tiimera tawhito

caption: It has a high stone wall with a barren stand and a barren set of stairs
orig: He pakitara koohatu teitei me tetahi tuunga pakoko me tetahi pakoko o nga huu

caption: It's a spicy Japanese food
orig: He kai tiapanii huuhii

caption: There is a food plate with a large variety of Japanese food on it
orig: He pereti kai me te rahi o nga momo kai Hapanihi kei runga

caption: A lying octopus
orig: He wheke e takoto ana

caption: White and brown squid on the sea floor
orig: He wheke maa me te parauri kei runga i te papa o te moana

caption: There is a church standing under the canopy of the sky, its banks are arrow houses, the road is people walking around in cars or under the road, there is a tree standing on the other side of the road.
orig: He whare karakia e tu ana i raro i te kahu o te rangi kai ona tahataha ko nga whare patu pere kai te rori ko nga tangata e haereere noa ana ma runga waka ma raro ranei kai tua o te rori he rakau e tu ana

caption: This is a video box that sits broken outside next to the houses where the banks are standing.
orig: He pouaka whitiarai tenei e noho whati ana i waho i te taha o nga whare kainga kai ona tahataha e tu ana

caption: The three women were standing next to an old car parked in the parking lot
orig: E tu ana nga wahine tokotoru nei i te taha o tetahi motuka tahito e tu ana i te tunga motuka

caption: This is a group of people who have gathered to look at the pictures hanging on the wall
orig: He kahui tangata tenei kua whakakao mai nei ki te tirotiro ki nga whakaahua e iri ana i te pakitara

caption: This is a long chair that sits in the middle of a synthetic building under a wall lamp with signs hanging on it
orig: He turu roa tenei e noho ana i waenga i te whare waihanga i raro i te rama kai te pakitara ko nga tohu e iri ana

caption: This is a warning sign placed under the food shelter after this sign that the weeds are growing
orig: He tohu whakatupato tenei e tu ana i raro i te whakaruruhau kai muri i te tohu nei ko nga tarutaru e tupu ana

caption: The people were standing in the museum and looking at the various items hanging on the walls a man in black clothes was standing there.
orig: E tu ana te hunga nei i roto i te whare taonga me te tirotiro tonu ki nga tini taonga e iri ana i ona pakitara e tu ana he taane i roto i ana kakahu pango

caption: This is a hotel swimming pool whose banks are bare, with umbrellas standing and tables and chairs spread out.
orig: He puna kauhoe tenei o te hotera e noho tahanga ana kai ona tahataha ko nga hamarara whakamarumaru e tu ana me nga tepu me nga turu e hora ana

caption: This is a modern sculpture that stands mockingly at the side of this terracotta building.
orig: He whakairo o te ao hou tenei e tu whakahi ana i te taha o tenei whare uku kai te tomokanga o te whare nei e tu ana he arapiki whakatika whare

caption: These are cooked foods that sit in a hot sauce that is served to eat
orig: He kai maoa enei e noho ana i roto i te hopane wera kua horahia nei ki te kai

caption: These are shelters that live at the foot of the bush, behind which the mountain ranges stand under the canopy of the sky, whose foundation is the spreading sand road.
orig: He pareparehua enei e noho ana i nga rekereke o te puihi e tu ana kai tua ko nga rarangi maunga e tu ana i raro i te kahu o te rangi kai te putake ko te ara kirikiri e hora ana

caption: These are a bunch of flowers sitting in a flower pot under bright lights with two women sitting beside them.
orig: He kohinga putiputi enei e noho ana i roto i te ipu putiputi i raro i nga rama wheriko kai ona tahataha nga wahine e rua e noho ana

caption: This is a racing car that is going fast on a racing road and on the other side of the road there is a guy standing alone
orig: He motuka reihi tenei e haere tere ana i runga i te rori reihi motuka kai tetahi taha o te rori he taane e tu takitahi ana

caption: This is a collection of vegetables wrapped in tomato slices and topped on a dinner plate
orig: He kohinga kai ngurara tenei kua takaia nei ki nga pihi tomato me te tihi i runga i te pereti kai

caption: This is a group of people entertaining themselves at a big party
orig: He huinga tangata tenei e whakangahau ana i a ratou ano i tetahi hui nui

caption: Today it is a church of the Purisha tribe with its carvings hanging from its walls and trees surrounding the entrance.
orig: Tenei ra he whare karakia no nga iwi puriha me ona whakairo e iri ana ki ona patuu a, e karapoti ana nga rakau i te tomokanga

caption: This is a black and white protest photo of a group of people holding protest flags.
orig: He whakaahua porotehi tenei kua tangia nei ki te pango me te ma e pupuri ana hoki te ope tangata i nga haki porotehi

caption: These are vegetables that are cooked in a pot until they are ready to eat
orig: Koinei nga huawhenua e tunua ana i roto i te kohua kia maoa kia rite ra ano mo te kai

caption: Airplane seats are empty and only a few people eat in the lower part of the plane
orig: Nga turu waka rererangi e tahanga ana tokoiti noaiho te hunga kai roto i te poho o te waka rererangi e noho ana

caption: There is a group of people eating by the water, picking food, each woman has a bowl, each woman eats their rings.
orig: He ope tenei kai te taha o te wai e kato ana i te kai he ipu to tena wahine to tena wahine kai o ratou ring

caption: These five men are sitting under a canopy that has been painted with beautiful colors
orig: E noho ana enei tane tokorima i raro i tetahi whakamarumaru kua tangia nei ki nga tae ataahua

caption: This is a rice roll from a Japanese restaurant spread out on a small plate
orig: He rora raihi tenei no te wharekai hapanihi kua rau atu i runga i tetahi pereti paku

caption: This car is parked outside the car park under the window of the building
orig: E tu ana tenei motuka i waho i te tunga motuka i raro i te pihanga o te whare nei

caption: This hat and clothes are hung on a plastic pole to make these clothes look beautiful
orig: Kua whakairia tenei potae me nga kakahu i runga i tetahi pou kirihou kia ataahua ai te hanga o nga kakahu nei

caption: This is a herd of deer eating grass in addition to standing trees and cars grazing its banks
orig: He ope tia tenei e kai ana i te patiti i tua atu ko nga rakau e tu ana me nga motuka kai ona tahataha

caption: This is a cow exploring the plain and on the sides there are many mountains
orig: He kau tenei e torotoro haere ana i te patiti nei a, kai nga taha ko nga tini maunga e tu ana

caption: It is an old church sheltered by trees with bells hanging from its spire
orig: He whare karakia tawhito kua whakamarumarutia nei ki nga rakau e iri ana hoki nga pere i tana pou kaiawha

caption: These are collections of books that have been laid out on the display table for sale to people
orig: He kohinga pukapuka enei kua rau atu i runga i te tepu hai tirohanga hai hokonga raanei mo te tangata

caption: The car's trunk and seats are now fringed with cowhide
orig: Te poho o te motuka me nga turu kua tanikohia nei ki te kiri o te kau

caption: These women are sitting together at their work place, the table is covered with paper, the spoon is a refrigerator, next to the refrigerator is a computer on the work surface.
orig: E hui ngatahi ana enei wahine i to ratou wahi mahi kai te tepu he pepa nui kua rorahia kai te koko he pouaka matao kai te taha o te pouaka matao e noho ana he rorohiko i runga i te pae mahi

caption: A cut piece of pine wood
orig: He poro raakau paaina kua tapahia

caption: It is a monument of the Christian religion
orig: He tohu whakamaumahara no tee haahi karaitiana

caption: There is a separate dining room on the terrace
orig: He kai motumotu kei runga i te riihi

caption: A group of people were waiting in the living room
orig: He roopu tangata e tatari ana i roto i te ruuma noho

caption: A couple is placed on a mountain
orig: He tokorua e tuu ana ki runga i te maunga

caption: A monkey apple landed on the floor
orig: He aaporo makimaki kua tau ki runga i te papa

caption: A green car is on the side of the road
orig: He motukaa kaakaariki kei te taha o te rori

caption: There is an old keyboard on the table
orig: He papa paatuhi tawhito kei runga i te teepu

caption: A chocolate drink in a black container
orig: He inu tiakarete i roto i te ipu pango

caption: A photo of some karate puppets
orig: He whakaahua o eetahi karetao karate

caption: A whale clings to a rock in the ocean
orig: He kina e piri ana ki te toka i roto i te moana

caption: A family of elephants drinking from a pitcher of water
orig: He whaanau arewhana e inu ana ki te hoopua wai

caption: A high bridge crosses the river
orig: He piriti teitei e whakawhiti ana i te awa

caption: A green bird clings to the end of a branch
orig: He manu kaakaariki e piri ana ki te pito o te peka

caption: A long bridge crosses the river in your late afternoon
orig: He piriti roa e whakawhiti ana i te awa i to ahiahi poo

caption: A photograph of a picture with corroded text
orig: He whakaahua o teetahi pikita kua waikura ngaa tuhinga

caption: A yellow lunch box contains rice
orig: He kai raihi kei roto i te pouaka tina koowhai

caption: A high-rise building in the middle of the city
orig: He whare teitei pourewa ki waenganui i te taaone

caption: A helicopter flies over the city
orig: He wakatopatopa e rere ana ki runga ake i te taaone

caption: It is a hilly country where trees are grown
orig: He whenua pukepuke e whakatipu raakau ana

caption: A statue of a woman lifting a star into the sky
orig: He whakapakoko o teetahi wahine hiki whetuu ki te rangi

caption: A couple takes a shower in the hotel pool
orig: He tokorua e kaukau ana ki te hoopuawai hooteera

caption: There is a black pass on the table
orig: He paahi pango kei runga i te teepu

caption: A mirror attached to the branches of a tree
orig: He whakaataata e piri ana ki ngaa peka o te raakau

caption: A Chinese woman with a remote is talking to her class
orig: He wahine hainamana mau remote e koorero ana ki tana karaehe

caption: There's a huge space machine coming into the room
orig: He mihiini aatea paatootoo e kaa mai ana ki te ruuma

caption: It's a donut bread with a sweet spread on top
orig: He paraaoa toonati me te pani reka ki runga

caption: Food wrapping paper with biographical information on it
orig: He pepa taakai kai me ngaa koorero taioranga ki runga

caption: A white hard hat with some red paint on it
orig: He pootae maaro maa me eetahi peita akakura ki runga

caption: A wood products store and owner operator
orig: He toa hoko hua raakau me te rangatira whakahaaere
